dataList.content: Feels like it’s getting colder and colder.
What’s up with all this ice around…?
An increase in the frequency of anomalies should ideally be strong, positive reflections.
*sigh* Am I missing some kind of pun here? Why do you keep reacting to that word? Gah, it's so cold...
Putting aside Ishmael’s grievance, I thought about what Faust had said.
<... Because that means we’re getting close to the Golden Bough… right, Faust?>
It was a pretty solid answer if I do say so myself.
Faust’s reply, however, was discouragingly dull, or at least that’s how it came across to me.
